00:17:02,300 --> 00:17:03,500
Warren Whispy說

300
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:05,500
先讀英文

301
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:10,100
Life is short and life is difficult

302
00:17:10,100 --> 00:17:15,500
so make the most of it while you can

303
